<A NAME=26Filler Trial>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Filler Trial</H3><BR>
AN F-B-I AGENT IS EXPECTED TO TESTIFY TODAY IN THE FORT ORD SNIPER ATTACK.
<P>
THE AGENT IS EXPECTED TO SAY THAT JOHN FILLER CONFESSED TO THE COMMITING THE SHOOTING AFTER HE WAS TAKEN INTO CUSTODY.
<P>
JAMES GAUGHRAN. THE MAN SHOT AND WOUNDED BY A FORT ORD SNIPER LAST JUNE. TOOK THE STAND IN THE CASE YESTERDAY.
<P>
GAUGHRAN. TOLD THE COURT HE NEVER WORKED WITH DEFENDANT JOHN FILLER.
<P>
HE DIDN'T EVEN KNOW THE MAN.
<P>
HE SAYS HE HEARD POPPING SOUNDS. JUST BEFORE FILLER TURNED A RIFLE ON HIM. 
<P>
IN: THIS MAN PUT. OC: TO BE ALIVE.
<P>
JOE LLOYD OF PRUNEDALE WAS KILLED DURING THAT AMBUSH.
<P>
GORAN PROUDLY TOLD THE COURT IT WAS LLOYD WHO SAVED HIS LIFE.
<P>

