<A NAME=27Salinas Shooting>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Salinas Shooting</H3><BR>
THE VICTIM OF A SHOOTING NEAR AN ELEMENTARY SCHOOL HAS BEEN IDENTIFIED.
<P>
19-YEAR-OLD JOSE FERNANDEZ FROM SALINAS WAS SHOT AND KILLED YESTERDAY ON NORTH SANBORN STREET AROUND 2-THIRTY IN THE MORNING.  
<P>
FERNANDEZ WAS REPORTEDLY WALKING DOWN THE STREET WHEN HE WAS CONFRONTED BY TWO MEN AND SHOT.
<P>
IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION YOUR ASKED TO CALL THE SALINAS POLICE DEPARTMENT.
<P>

