<A NAME=28Hwy 17 187 Update>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Hwy 17 187 Update</H3><BR>
AUTHORITIES HAVE IDENTIFIED THE WOMAN WHOSE BODY WAS FOUND FRIDAY IN THE SANTA CRUZ MOUNTAINS.
<P>
SHE IS 38-YEAR OLD DEBBIE MACKAY.AND HER HUSBAND IS UNDER ARREST FOR MURDER.
<P>
POLICE ARRESTED DAN MACKAY AFTER FINDING HIM STANDING NEXT TO HIS STALLED, BLOOD-SPLATTERED TRUCK ON THE SIDE OF HIGHWAY 17.
<P>
MACKAY THEN LED OFFICERS TO HIS WIFE'S BODY.
<P>
FREMONT POLICE SAY THE COUPLE'S FOUR CHILDREN ARE NOW STAYING WITH RELATIVES.
<P>

