<A NAME=29Teacher Protest>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Teacher Protest</H3><BR>
CONTROVERSY THIS MORNING AT THE SALINAS CITY SCHOOL DISTRICT.
<P>
ANGRY PARENTS AND TEACHERS STAGED A PROTEST YESTERDAY OVER A SCHOOL BOARD DECISION. TO DEMOTE AN ELEMENTARY SCHOOL PRINCIPAL
<P>
MARY SEIRSEN IS THE PRINCIPAL FOR EL GABILAN ELEMENTARY SCHOOL.
<P>
LAST MONTH THE SCHOOL BOARD DEMOTED HER TO TEACHER. SAYING SHE LOST CONFIDENCE IN THE POSITION.
<P>
SEIRSEN SAYS THERE MAY BE OTHER MOTIVES.
<P>
"I FILED A DISCRIMINATION HARRASSMENT COMPLAINT WITH THE DISTRICT, SO SINCE THERE HASN'T BEEN ANYTHING ELSE. I BELIEVE IT'S RETALIATION."
<P>
"PROBABLY TO OTHER PEOPLE. IT DOESNT' MATTER. BUT IT COULD HAPPEN TO THEIR PRINCIPAL TOO."
<P>
THE BOARD HAS DENIED THE DISCRIMINATION COMPLAINT.
<P>
MEANWHILE. SEIRSEN HAS FORMALLY ASKED THE SCHOOL BOARD TO RESCIND ITS DECISION AND REINSTATE HER BACK TO PRINCIPAL. 
<P>

