<A NAME=37Care Center Fire >
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Care Center Fire </H3><BR>
FIVE PEOPLE ARE DEAD THIS MORNING FOLLOWING A LATE NIGHT FIRE AT A HOME FOR THE ELDERLY NEAR SEATTLE.
<P>
THE BLAZE WAS QUICKLY CONTAINED BUT FIREFIGHTERS SAY MOST OF THE WOOD FRAME BUILDING WAS FILLED WITH HOT GAS AND BLACK SMOKE BY THE TIME THEY ARRIVED AT THE SCENE.
<P>
23 PEOPLE HAVE BEEN TAKEN TO THE HOSPITAL.MOST OF THEM WITH MINOR INJURIES.
<P>
THE 90-YEAR-OLD BUILDING THAT WAS CONVERTED INTO A CENTER FOR THE ELDERLY REPORTEDLY HAD NO SPRINKLERS INSTALLED INSIDE.
<P>
FIRE INVESTIGATORS ARE STILL TRYING TO DETERMINE THE CAUSE OF THE DEADLY BLAZE.
<P>

