<A NAME=25Teacher Buried>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Teacher Buried</H3><BR>
THE PENNSYLVANIA MIDDLE SCHOOL TEACHER WHO WAS GUNNED DOWN BY A STUDENT FRIDAY NIGHT WILL BE LAID TO REST TODAY.
<P>
AT LEAST TWO THOUSAND PEOPLE ARE EXPECTED TO SAY GOODBYE AT A FUNERAL SERVICE FOR JOHN GILLETTE IN EDINBORO, PENNSYLVANIA.
<P>
COUNSELORS WERE ON HAND YESTERDAY AT THE MIDDLE SCHOOL TO HELP STUDENTS COPE WITH THEIR EMOTIONS.
<P>
MEANWHILE POLICE HAVE CHARGED 14-YEAR-OLD ANDREW WURST WITH THE SCIENCE TEACHER'S SHOOTING DEATH.
<P>

