<A NAME=24Caught on Tape>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Caught on Tape</H3><BR>
LIKE A GENIE GOING BACK INTO HIS LAMP.THE ALADDIN HOTEL CASINO IN LAS VAGAS DISAPPEARED IN A CLOUD OF SMOKE YESTERDAY.
<P>
THE 17 STORY BUILDING WAS IMPLODED BY A SERIES OF STRATEGICALLY PLACED EXPLOSIVES.
<P>
THE HOTEL CASINO HAD ITS PLACE IN HISTORY.ROCK LEGEND ELVIS PRESLEY MARRIED PARCILLA PRESLEY THERE IN 19-67.
<P>
THE ALADDIN FOLLOWS OTHER LAS VEGAS HOTELS WHICH HAVE MET THE SAME FATE TO MAKE ROOM FOR  LARGER AND IMPROVED HOTEL CASINOS.
<P>
A NEWER VERSION OF THE ALADDIN WILL BE CONSTRUCTED ON THE SAME SITE, AND ITS EXPECTED TO OPEN IN THE YEAR TWO THOUSAND.
<P>

