<A NAME=19Tomb of Unknown>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Tomb of Unknown</H3><BR>
A PENTAGON PANEL IS RECOMMENDING THAT THE REMAINS OF AN AIR FORCE PILOT WHO WAS SHOT DOWN OVER SOUTH VIETNAM IN 19-72 BE EXHUMED.
<P>
THE PANEL WANTS TO MAKE SURE THAT THE REMAINS OF THE DOWNED PILOT AREN'T THOSE OF MICHAEL BLASSIE AS ONCE THOUGHT.
<P>
THE REMAINS ARE BURIED IN THE TOMB OF THE UNKNOWNS, A MONUMENT THAT'S DEDICATED TO THE NATION'S UNIDENTIFIED WAR DEAD.
<P>
THE BLASSIE FAMILY IS ALSO ASKING THE DEFENSE DEPARTMENT TO EXHUME THE REMAINS FOR D-N-A TESTING.
<P>

