CARTER WAS ON HAND AT A CEREMONY AT THE PENTAGON'S CENTRAL COURTYARD YESTERDAY.
<P>
THE FORMER PRESIDENT CALLED THE NAMING CEREMONY ONE OF HIS PROUDEST DAYS.
<P>

